//! Specific Test Implementations
//!
//! Contains concrete test implementations for each API endpoint/feature.
//!
//! ## Entity Test Coverage
//!
//! Entity-specific tests will be generated by the schema generator:
//! ```bash
//! metaphor schema generate {{MODULE_NAME}} --target all
//! ```
//!
//! | Entity               | Module                      | Status |
//! |----------------------|-----------------------------|--------|
//! | {{ENTITY_NAME}}      | {{entity_name}}_api_test    | TODO   |
//!
//! ## Adding Custom Tests
//!
//! Create entity-specific test files in this directory:
//! ```
//! tests/integration/tests/
//! ├── mod.rs                    # This file
//! ├── crud_test_base.rs         # Generic CRUD test base (generated)
//! └── {{entity_name}}_api_test.rs  # Entity-specific tests (generated)
//! ```

// Generic CRUD test base will be generated here
// pub mod crud_test_base;

// Entity-specific tests will be generated here
// pub mod {{entity_name}}_api_test;
